## Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] Echo prevention: envelopes from `relay.human.slack.*` are skipped
- [ ] Returns error when client is null
- [ ] First `text_delta` starts a new message via `chat.postMessage`, subsequent ones update via `chat.update`
- [ ] `done` event finalizes the stream and cleans up streamState
- [ ] `error` event appends error text and finalizes (or posts standalone error)
- [ ] Silent event types are skipped
- [ ] Standard payloads are sent via `chat.postMessage` with mrkdwn conversion
- [ ] Messages are truncated to MAX_MESSAGE_LENGTH (4000 chars)
- [ ] All bot responses include `thread_ts` for threading
- [ ] All tests pass

